platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: The line never ends at Dr. Pandas Ice Cream Truck, and thats just how our kids like it. They jump at the chance to whip up new flavors and serve sky-high sundaes piled with toppings. Watching customers gobble down their desserts cracks them up every time (and us too).

The line never ends at Dr. Pandas Ice Cream Truck, and thats just how our kids like it. They jump at the chance to whip up new flavours and serve sky-high sundaes piled with toppings. Watching customers gobble down their desserts cracks them up every time (and us too).

Crer toutes les glaces de son choix, empiler les parfums, les nappages et les garnitures, cookies, fruits, noix... avec pour seules limites son imagination et sa gourmandise. Le rve ! Cest tellement amusant de prparer des cornets garnis de boules multicolores et encore plus drle de voir les ractions des diffrents animaux quand ils les gotent !
